quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  17,71,"On the Day We summon every people with their records, those who are given their Book in their right hand will read their Book and they will not be wronged by even the smallest speck"
  17,72,Those who are blind in this world will be blind in the Next World and even further off the Path
  17,73,"They were very near to enticing you away from some of what We have revealed to you, hoping that you would invent something against Us. Then they would have taken you as their intimate"
  17,74,"If We had not made you firm, you would have leaned towards them a little"
  17,75,Then We would have let you taste a double punishment in life and a double punishment in death. You would not have found any helper against Us
  17,76,They were very near to scaring you from the land with the object of expelling you from it. But had they done so they would only have remained there a short time after you
  17,77,That was the pattern with those We sent before you as Our Messengers. You will not find any changing of Our pattern